Sealed here is Ioannes[[footnote]]Latin for John.[[/footnote]] the Unbroken, betrayer of us all. Heretic consumer of a fragment of her [http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-882 heart]. A son of the true God corrupted by her opposite.

Twice we failed to destroy him. Twice we could only foist his corruption upon another world. May a third chance never arrive.

Should we falter in our vigil, then you our successor must rise in our place. Use the visions. They are our greatest feat, and the keys to your victory.
[[/collapsible]]
[[collapsible show="Adytite Translation" hide="Close Translation"]]
[[div style="border: 1px solid black;
